Text:
Went to Amazon for this, and was shocked at the $42 price tag. Seriously, Amazon, go fuck yourself. Does it come with a large breasted blonde to read it to me? 
Straight to TPB and 20 minutes later I have it. 
To the audio book industry - I tried, you failed.
It seems that Part 9 is incomplete. But when I checked with the original text, it is actually NOT. The end of Part 9 and the beginning of part 10 is actually correct! Thanks uploader!
Thank you for release, but I'll wait for higher quality version. There are just too many compression artifacts to enjoy listening.
